# [[multitude]] of grass
#* [http://ctext.org/shuo-wen-jie-zi/mang-bu#n26876 Shuo Wen Jie Zi] (a dictionary in East Han Dynasty)
#* {{zh-x|茻：眾 艸 也。从 四 屮。凡 茻 之 屬 皆 从 茻。讀 與 冈 同。|[The character] 茻 [means] multiple grass indeed. [The character is] composed [of] four 屮. All that belongs to the 茻 radical are composed of 茻. [The character's] pronunciation is the same as 冈.|CL}}
